snippet.title: Castle In The Darkness 2 Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Matt Kap and Simon Parzer are happy to announce that the sequel to 2015's Castle In The Darkness is now in development at LABS Works!
We will be releasing a mini-trailer for this game on the 2nd of every month, so please follow LABS on social media so you don't miss the surprises!

Twitter- http://www.twitter.com/LABSworks
Facebook- http://www.facebook.com/LABSworks
Instagram- http://www.instagram.com/labsworks

LABS Works website- http://labs.works

Matt's twitter- http://www.twitter.com/Mattkap1
Simon's twitter- http://www.twitter.com/simonparzer

Media Contact: pr@labs.works
